All Implemented Interfaces:
SubstitutionModel, Model, ModelListener, StatisticList, VariableListener, MPISerializable, Identifiable, java.io.Serializable
public class TN93
extends AbstractNucleotideModel

Tamura and Nei model of nucleotide evolution.

pr = p[0]+p[1] py = 1 - pr

eigen values

[0, -1, -(k[0]*pr + py), -(k[1]*py + pr)]

unnormalized eigen vectors [1,1,1,1], [1,1,-pr/py,-pr/py], [1, -p[0]/p[1], 0, 0], [0, 0, 1,-p[2]/p[3]]

Author:
Joseph Heled
